OL,3,CPreston Davey murder trial hears
OL,4,Cdefence barristers' closing speeches
OL,6,FJurors have been told it would be
OL,7,F"tragic" to convict a teacher of
OL,8,Fmurdering his adopted baby boy on a
OL,9,F"gap" in evidence filled with emotion.
OL,11,FJamie Varley, 37, denies the killing
OL,12,Fof 13-month-old Preston Davey
OL,13,Ffollowing months of alleged physical
OL,14,Fand sexual abuse.
OL,16,FHis partner, John McGowan-Fazakerley,
OL,17,F32, denies causing or allowing the
OL,18,Fdeath of the child, cruelty and sexual
OL,19,Fassault.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@HO]qD@AOUqD@EO]
