OL,3,CPreston Davey murder trial hears
OL,4,Cdefence barristers' closing speeches
OL,6,FBoth men deny a sexual interest in the
OL,7,Fchild and have pleaded not guilty to
OL,8,Fall charges during the seven-week
OL,9,Ftrial at Preston Crown Court.
OL,11,FNick Johnson KC, defending Varley, in
OL,12,Fhis closing speech to the jury said:
OL,13,F"This will always be a deeply tragic,
OL,14,Fshocking case and we can't bring
OL,15,FPreston back.
OL,17,F"It would be even more tragic to
OL,18,Fconvict a man of previous good
OL,19,Fcharacter from evidence where you are
OL,20,Ffilling the gap with emotion."
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
