OL,3,CPreston Davey murder trial hears
OL,4,Cdefence barristers' closing speeches
OL,6,FPreston was adopted by Varley, a high
OL,7,Fschool head of year, and McGowan-
OL,8,FFazakerley, a financial sales manager,
OL,9,Fin April 2023 and in the next four
OL,10,Fmonths living at their home in
OL,11,FBlackpool, it is alleged he suffered
OL,12,Fsexual abuse and ill-treatment.
OL,14,FThe child was rushed to Blackpool
OL,15,FVictoria Hospital on July 27, with
OL,16,FVarley telling medical staff he had
OL,17,Fleft the child in the bath for two or
OL,18,Fthree minutes and returned to find him
OL,19,Fsubmerged.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
