OL,3,CPreston Davey murder trial hears
OL,4,Cdefence barristers' closing speeches
OL,6,FBut prosecutors allege this was a
OL,7,Fcover story to explain his sudden
OL,8,Fdeath after a sexual assault.
OL,10,FA post-mortem examination found 40
OL,11,Fexternal and internal trauma injuries
OL,12,Fto the child's body, consistent with
OL,13,F"forcible penetration" and sexual
OL,14,Fabuse, and ruled out drowning as a
OL,15,Fcause of death.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
