PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781046184
OL,3,CPreston Davey murder trial hears
OL,4,Cdefence barristers' closing speeches
OL,6,FMr Johnson told jurors Preston's cause
OL,7,Fof death was initially unascertained
OL,8,Fand he suggested the prosecution
OL,9,F"theory" he died from acute airway
OL,10,Fobstruction by an object or object
OL,11,Fplaced in his mouth was based on a
OL,12,F"rigid" interpretation of
OL,13,Fcircumstantial evidence amounting to
OL,14,F"scientific speculation".
OL,16,FHe suggested both internal and
OL,17,Fexternal bruises found on the child's
OL,18,Fbody could be explained by the
OL,19,F"frantic" efforts of hospital staff to
OL,20,Fsave his life.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@HO]tD@AOUtD@GO]vD@AOUvD@XO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
