OL,3,CPreston Davey murder trial hears
OL,4,Cdefence barristers' closing speeches
OL,6,FMr Johnson said Varley would have to
OL,7,Fbe a sophisticated criminal
OL,8,F"mastermind" to have hid the physical
OL,9,Fand sexual abuse of the child, who was
OL,10,Fbeing seen by health and social
OL,11,Fworkers whose job it was to spot red
OL,12,Fflags and who raised a "no hint" of
OL,13,Fconcern.
OL,15,FAnne Whyte KC, defending McGowan-
OL,16,FFazakerley, said the defendants were
OL,17,F"two very different individuals".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@LO]tD@XOUtD@`O]yD@AOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
