OL,3,CPreston Davey murder trial hears
OL,4,Cdefence barristers' closing speeches
OL,6,F"It's not good enough to find someone
OL,7,Fguilty by association."
OL,9,FVarley denies murder, manslaughter,
OL,10,Ftwo counts of assault by penetration,
OL,11,Ffive counts of cruelty to a child,
OL,12,Fgrievous bodily harm, sexual assault
OL,13,Fof a child, 13 counts of taking
OL,14,Findecent photos or videos of a child,
OL,15,Fone of distributing an indecent photo
OL,16,Fof a child, to his co-accused, and one
OL,17,Fof making an indecent photo.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@WO]
