OL,3,CPreston Davey murder trial hears
OL,4,Cdefence barristers' closing speeches
OL,6,FMcGowan-Fazakerley denies allowing the
OL,7,Fdeath of a child, three counts of
OL,8,Fchild cruelty and one count of the
OL,9,Fsexual assault of a child.
OL,11,FThe jury is now down to 10, after two
OL,12,Fjurors were discharged for medical and
OL,13,Ffamily-related reasons yesterday and
OL,14,Ftoday.
OL,16,FThe trial was adjourned until 10.30am
OL,17,Fon Thursday for the judge to sum up
OL,18,Fthe case before they are expected to
OL,19,Fretire to consider verdicts later that
OL,20,Fday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
